<meta content='https://www.blogger.com/profile/07772713854922384990' itemprop='url'/>
<a class='g-profile' href='https://www.blogger.com/profile/07772713854922384990' rel='author' title='author profile'>
<span itemprop='name'>Sakti Deb</span>
</a>
</span>
</span>
<span class='post-timestamp'>
at
<meta content='http://indiadying.blogspot.com/2018/03/they-are-escaping-because-they-can.html' itemprop='url'/>
<a class='timestamp-link' href='https://indiadying.blogspot.com/2018/03/they-are-escaping-because-they-can.html' rel='bookmark' title='permanent link'><abbr class='published' itemprop='datePublished' title='2018-03-19T22:39:00-07:00'>10:39 PM</abbr></a>
</span>
<span class='reaction-buttons'>
</span>
<span class='post-comment-link'>
<a class='comment-link' href='https://www.blogger.com/comment.g?blogID=30383592&postID=251917765936041112&isPopup=true' onclick='javascript:window.open(this.href, "bloggerPopup", "toolbar=0,location=0,statusbar=1,menubar=0,scrollbars=yes,width=640,height=500"); return false;'>
No comments:
  </a>
</span>
<span class='post-backlinks post-comment-link'>
<a class='comment-link' href='https://indiadying.blogspot.com/2018/03/they-are-escaping-because-they-can.html#links'>Links to this post</a>
</span>
<span class='post-icons'>
<span class='item-control blog-admin pid-56306591'>
